Levels Beyond Assessment:

Used Technologies:

Java, Jersey Rest, Hibernate, MYSQL, Apache Tomcat.

Steps to Run the program:

Step 1:
Run the sql dump file before executing the program. It will create the tables and the schema in the MySQL DB.
Schema Name-levelsbeyond.
Table Name-notes

Step 2: Storing a note into DB

Deploy the web application in the apache tomcat server.

Step 3: Storing
For Persisting Data into Database: Method: POST Accept format: JSON

http://localhost:8080/api/notes

example input in JSON Format: {"body" : "Pick up milk!"}

recieves: {
    "id": 6,
    "body": "values"
}

Step 4: Reading all

For Reading all notes: Method: GET

http://localhost:8080/api/notes/getallnotes

Step 5: Reading by id

For Reading specific notes by id, Method: GET

http://localhost:8080/api/notes/1

Step 6: Reading wildcard

For getting wildcards query Method: GET

http://localhost/api/notes?query=forget